author: Benoît Faucon
title: Algeria Writes to OPEC Over Falling Oil Prices
text:
Algeria has written to OPEC warning that a new drop in oil prices may warrant fresh discussions over the group’s strategy, people familiar with the matter said, the latest sign of economic stress for some members of the cartel.
